Name: Mickey Ward-El Smith
Description:
Mickey was shot ten times.

> My name is Mickey Ward-El Smith, and I was a nineteen year old transperson living in Washington, D.C.
>
> I was shot ten times at Saratoga and twenty-fifth Streets NE, on March third. My wig had also been removed.
>
> Unlike other recent anti-transgender murders in Washington, DC, very little seems to have been done about my death.
